com.carteryagemann.AICS

Class IntentData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.carteryagemann.AICS.IntentData

  • public class IntentData
extends java.lang.Object
    An object for storing the contents of an Android intent. It should be combined with an intent header to create a complete packet which can then be stored inside an AICS file.
